- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses variations and improvements of the codes. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the codes are based on evaluating polynomials and their derivatives. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of decoding algorithms for these codes. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the geometric interpretation of the codes.
